---
title: Sesame Crusted Chicken with Buttery Rice and Sweet Plum Chili sauce
description: Tuxedo-crusted chicken drizzled with a sweet sticky plum and chili sauce takes center stage in tonight's chicken special! Buttery rice, topped with roasted sweet carrots is the perfect co-star.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-en-croute-de-sesame-5e7bf34f.jpg
